  ${
    $d f k m n x A $.  $d f m n x B $.  $d f m n x C $.
    $( Equality theorem for sum, with the class expressions ` B ` and ` C `
       guarded by ` _I ` to be always sets.  (Contributed by Mario Carneiro,
