  ${
    $d f k m n x A $.  $d f m n x B $.  $d f m n x C $.
    $( Equality theorem for sum.  (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 13-Jul-2013.) $)
    sumeq2 $p |- ( A. k e. A B = C -> sum_ k e. A B = sum_ k e. A C ) $=
      ( wceq wral cid cfv csu fveq2 ralimi sumeq2ii syl ) BCEZDAFBGHCGHEZDAFABD
      IACDIENODABCGJKABCDLM $.
