    $d A j k $.  $d B k $.  $d C j $.
    $( Change bound variable in a sum.  (Contributed by Mario Carneiro,
       13-Jul-2013.) $)
    cbvsumv $p |- sum_ j e. A B = sum_ k e. A C $=
      ( vx cv wcel ax-17 cbvsum ) GABCDEFGHZAIZEJMDJLBIEJLCIDJK $.
