  ${
    $d j A $.  $d k B $.  $d k C $.  $d j k M $.  $d j k N $.  $d j k ph $.
    $d k D $.  $d k E $.
    fsumtscop.1 $e |- ( k = j -> A = B ) $.
    fsumtscop.2 $e |- ( k = ( j + 1 ) -> A = C ) $.
    fsumtscop.3 $e |- ( k = M -> A = D ) $.
    fsumtscop.4 $e |- ( k = ( N + 1 ) -> A = E ) $.
    fsumtscop.5 $e |- ( ph -> N e. ZZ ) $.
    fsumtscop.6 $e |- ( ph -> ( N + 1 ) e. ( ZZ>= ` M ) ) $.
    fsumtscop.7 $e |- ( ( ph /\ k e. ( M ... ( N + 1 ) ) ) -> A e. CC ) $.
    $( Sum of a telescoping series.  (Contributed by Scott Fenton,
       24-Apr-2014.)  (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 15-Jun-2014.) $)
